sentence: The following companies are expected to report earnings after hours on 11/27/2018.

The computer software company's consensus earnings per share forecast from the 14 analysts that follow the stock is $0.15.
This value represents a no change for the same quarter last year.
In the past year CRM has beat the expectations every quarter.
